            "content": [
              {
                "component": "Text",
                "content": "# Next level\n\nYour mind is like a friend, always looking out for you, constantly sending warnings and tips. But just as you wouldn't always do what your friends tell you, you don't always need to react to a thought you have. \n\nThoughts are thoughts – they are not always true."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "component": "ButtonGroup",
            "content": [
              {
                "component": "Button",
                "content": "Got it",
                "conversationId": "relationships-thingsgowrong-3",
                "sectionId": "2"
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
        "type": "defaultSection"
      },
      {
        "id": "2",
        "alias": "2",
        "content": [
          {
            "component": "TextGroup",
            "content": [
              {
                "component": "Text",
                "content": "Practice **allowing** a thought to pass like yet another cloud in the sky.\n\nSometimes you will need to act on your thoughts to look after yourself, but not always. Sometimes it is just your mind trying to help you out – even if  you didn't ask for it."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
